value.0: A helmet worn by the common soldiers and guards of Stormhaven.  It is sturdy, reliable, and padded with a thin layer of cloth and wool to keep the wearer warm in the highland climates.
Armor worn by the guards and common soldiers of Stormhaven.  Sturdy and reliable, local smiths who manage to provide quality such as this are well paid by the Highlord.
Masterwork weapons and armor are the product of the world's finest craftsman and surpass even some enchanted items in strength and ability.

Like most of a Stormhaven Guard's arsenal, these weapons are specially crafted to aid against some of the common monstrous entities that are drawn to corrupted locations due to excessive arcane influence.
Made from the heavy furs of Ebon Spire wolves, these cloaks are a boon against the more frigid Northern elements.
